        "subject": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in command parser",
        "message": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize error messages in command parser\n\nError messages for the command parser are updated to a standard\nformat.  The message is prefixed with the name of the utility\nand the command that caused the error.  User-provided values are\ndelimited with single quotes.\n\nWhen incorrect options or parameters are provided to a command,\nthe full help text is no longer printed.  Instead, a brief message\nis displayed asking the user to consult the help.\n\nWhen help is requested for a command, the help for any associated\nsub-commands is displayed along with it.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Steve Guminski <stephenx.guminski@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9b6806e34b1e31eebb18f9162d90930c836d0266\n"
      },
